## 🎨 Custom CSS Usage (Admin Web)

### Custom CSS Rules

**MUST:**

- ✅ Place custom CSS in `shared/styles/admin/`
- ✅ Use `@layer components` for component styles
- ✅ Use `@apply` directive to extend Tailwind
- ✅ Follow BEM-like naming for custom classes
- ✅ Import CSS files at the top of component files

**Example:**

```css
/* src/shared/styles/admin/search-form.css */
.search-form-label {
  @apply justify-end pr-4 font-bold;
}
```

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Create global styles without `@layer`
- ❌ Use `!important` without justification
- ❌ Duplicate Tailwind functionality in custom CSS
- ❌ Forget to import CSS files in components

