## 📋 Search Form Structure (Admin Web)

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: 조회조건 폼 구조 패턴

**MUST ALWAYS use this structure for search forms in admin list pages:**

**Structure Pattern:**

```typescript
{
  /* 모바일 조회조건 토글 버튼 */
}
<div className="md:hidden mb-2">
  <button onClick={() => setShowSearchForm(!showSearchForm)}>
    {showSearchForm ? "▲ 조회조건 닫기" : "▼ 조회조건 열기"}
  </button>
</div>;

{
  /* 조회조건 폼 컨테이너 */
}
<div
  className={`bg-white mb-3 rounded-lg shadow search-form-container ${
    showSearchForm ? "show" : ""
  }`}
>
  <div className="border border-gray-300">
    {/* 검색구분 + 검색어 입력 필드만 */}
    <div className="flex flex-wrap">
      <div className="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div className="flex flex-col border-b md:flex-row items-stretch">
          <label className="w-full md:w-1/4 bg-gray-100 flex items-center m-0 px-3 py-2 search-form-label border-b border-r border-gray-300">
            검색구분
          </label>
          <div className="w-full md:w-3/4 flex p-2">{/* SELECT + INPUT */}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>;

{
  /* 조회 버튼은 폼 밖에 별도 배치 */
}
<div className="flex justify-end mb-3 gap-2">
  <button onClick={handleSearch}>🔍 조회</button>
</div>;
```

**MUST:**

- ✅ Search form container: Contains only search fields (select + input)
- ✅ Action buttons (조회): Placed OUTSIDE the form container, in a separate `div` with `flex justify-end mb-3 gap-2`
- ✅ Import `@/shared/styles/admin/search-form.css` for `search-form-label` styles

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Place action buttons inside the search form container
- ❌ Create inconsistent structures across different admin list pages
- ❌ Forget to import `search-form.css` (causes text alignment issues)

**Reference Implementation:**

- ✅ `src/features/adminWeb/program/list/ui/ProgramListPageView.tsx` (reference implementation)

**Common Mistakes:**

1. **Placing buttons inside form container:**

   ```typescript
   // ❌ WRONG: Button inside form container
   <div className="search-form-container">
     {/* fields */}
     <div className="flex justify-end p-2 border-t">
       <button>조회</button>  {/* ❌ Wrong location */}
     </div>
   </div>

   // ✅ CORRECT: Button outside form container
   <div className="search-form-container">
     {/* fields only */}
   </div>
   <div className="flex justify-end mb-3 gap-2">
     <button>조회</button>  {/* ✅ Correct location */}
   </div>
   ```

2. **Missing CSS import:**

   ```typescript
   // ❌ WRONG: Missing CSS import
   import { useMenuMakeList } from '../model';
   // Missing: import "@/shared/styles/admin/search-form.css";

   // ✅ CORRECT: CSS import present
   import { useMenuMakeList } from '../model';
   import '@/shared/styles/admin/search-form.css';
   ```

