## 💡 Key Principles

1. **Consistency First**: ALL register buttons MUST look identical across all admin pages
2. **Visual Recognition**: Consistent icons help users quickly identify action buttons
3. **Professional Appearance**: Inconsistent buttons look unprofessional and untested
4. **Maintainability**: Standardized buttons are easier to maintain and update
5. **User Experience**: Users expect consistent UI patterns across the application

