### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Attachment File Row Structure

**MUST ALWAYS use this structure for attachment file UI in admin registration/edit forms when:**

- ✅ Adding file upload to registration forms (e.g., article, board)
- ✅ Displaying a list of selected files with remove action
- ✅ Using extension-based file type icons
