- **Register:** `src/features/adminWeb/article/register/ui/ArticleRegisterForm.tsx`, `useArticleRegister.ts`
- **Edit/Detail:** `src/features/adminWeb/article/detail/ui/ArticleDetailForm.tsx`, `src/features/adminWeb/article/detail/model/useArticleDetail.ts`

Use these for state shape, FormData construction, and post-update clearing; adapt field names and limits to the feature’s API.

